     <div type="poem">
   <head>EPITAPHIUM <hi>ROSAE</hi> ad viatorem.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>Quid stupeas qui prata vides defesse viator,</l>
      <l>Quod pereat nostri gratia tanta <hi>Rosae?</hi>
      </l>
      <l>Nam{que} rosâ nil est brevius, properantius aevi,</l>
      <l>Nil, ut mane viret, sole cadente perit.</l>
      <l>
         <pb facs="65"/>
Pulchralicet durat sugitivo tempore, Nonne</l>
      <l>Nutrit &amp; vna dies, tollit &amp; unarosam?</l>
      <l>Haecque tuae formae species, haec lucis imago</l>
      <l>Viva docet vitam sic properare tuam.</l>
      <l>Ʋt qui pubescis primo nunc flore juventae,</l>
      <l>Moximproviso curva senecta premat,</l>
      <l>Sis niveâ rutilâ{que} rosâter pulchrior, ora</l>
      <l>Inficiet pallor, funereus{que} color.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <dateline>Anno <date>1634. idus Octobr.</date>
      </dateline>
      <signed>NINIANUS CAMPBELLUS.</signed>
   </closer>
   <pb facs="65"/>
</div>
